{"article_id":"iCIPSFv376rLSRX3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A Chicago judge set Jussie Smollett 's bond at $ 100,000 on Thursday","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"and ordered him to surrender his passport ,","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"hours after a remarkable Chicago Police Department press conference","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"in which Superintendent Eddie T. Johnson blasted the 'Empire ' star ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that Smollett 's alleged staging of a hoax attack was a `` publicity stunt ...","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"to promote his career . ''","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Interested in Jussie Smollett ?","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Add Jussie Smollett as an interest","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Jussie Smollett news , video , and analysis from .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Add Interest","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"The weeks-long investigation into the alleged hate crime attack","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"-- an alarming account","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that sizzled with a spectrum of hot button issues","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"ranging from race , sexuality and politics to crime and celebrity --","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"riveted and distressed a deeply-divided nation .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"Standing before Cook County Circuit Court Judge John Fitzgerald Lyke , Jr. ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Smollett appeared to remain steadfast in his refutation of the felony charge against him .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"He has repeatedly insisted","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that the attack was real","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"and that he was merely a victim , not a perpetrator .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"If convicted of felony disorderly conduct","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"for filing a false report ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"the actor faces up to three years in prison .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"When first assistant state attorney Risa Lanier told Lyke","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"that the actor had picked up two brothers","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"who","depth":16},{"id":27,"text":"authorities say","depth":16},{"id":28,"text":"carried out the staged attack on him at his direction","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"and showed them the location","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"of where he wanted to be attacked ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"Smollett shook his head in disagreement .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"When Lyke told Smollett","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"that the allegations ,","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"if true ,","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"are `` utterly outrageous , ''","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"the actor nodded his head in agreement","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"-- doing so again","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"when Lyke said","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"the noose detail would be the most despicable part of the alleged scheme .","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"The judge also ordered pre-trial monitoring of the actor ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"and ordered him to stay away from the two brothers","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"he allegedly conspired with","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"to stage the hoax attack ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"according to police .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The tense courtroom appearance followed on the heels of a morning press conference","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"at which a visibly angry Johnson castigated the actor","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"for betraying his race and his city with such an incendiary false claim .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"`` Jussie Smollett took advantage of the pain and anger of racism","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"to promote his career , ''","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"a visibly angry Johnson said .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"\" I am left hanging my head","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"asking ' why ? ' .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Why would anyone ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"especially an African-American man , use the symbolism of a noose","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"to make false accusations ?","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"... How can an individual","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"who 's been embraced by the city of Chicago","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"turn around and slap everyone in the city in the face with these false claims ? ''","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"Johnson charged","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that Smollett , an actor on the hit show 'Empire '","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"who has consistently denied any role","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"in staging the alleged attack ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"orchestrated it","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"because he was `` dissatisfied with his salary . ''","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"In addition to staging the attack ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"officials said ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Smollett also sent himself a hate-filled letter to the Fox studio","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"where the hit show is filmed .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Smollett turned himself in at 5:15 a.m. local time","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"and made a statement to police","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"before being taken into custody .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"His lawyers , Todd Pugh and Victor Henderson , were not present at the time","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"but they released a statement the night before .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"`` Like any other citizen , Mr. Smollett enjoys the presumption of innocence ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"particularly when there has been an investigation like this one","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"where information ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"both true and false ,","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"has been repeatedly leaked .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Given these circumstances , we intend to conduct a thorough investigation","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"and to mount an aggressive defense . ''","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Thursday evening , the attorneys released a statement","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"criticizing law enforcement 's handling of the case .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"`` Today we witnessed an organized law enforcement spectacle","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"that has no place in the American legal system .","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"The presumption of innocence , a bedrock in the search for justice , was trampled upon at the expense of Mr. Smollett and notably , on the eve of a Mayoral election , ''","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"the statement read .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"`` Mr. Smollett is a young man of impeccable character and integrity","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"who fiercely and solemnly maintains his innocence","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"and feels betrayed by a system","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"that apparently wants to skip due process","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"and proceed directly to sentencing . ''","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"Police add","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"that Smollett gave no statement to police","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"after turning himself in","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and that his lawyers had reached out to them Wednesday night","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"to discuss his surrender .","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"Smollett wanted to turn himself in near midnight ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"but authorities suggested","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"he come in at 5 a.m. instead ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"to avoid spending the night in jail .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Smollett arrived early Thursday morning","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"accompanied by a female lawyer and an entourage of five or six people .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Smollett was silent","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"as he went through the motions","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"of being booked and processed .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"By late morning on Thursday , the backlash against the actor began at the top , with an angry tweet from the President of the United States .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"`` .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"@ JussieSmollett - what about MAGA and the tens of millions of people","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"you insulted with your racist and dangerous comments ! ?","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"# MAGA ''","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"President Donald Trump wrote in a tweet after the press conference .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"In an earlier interview with , Smollett was asked why he thought","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"he was targeted","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and he replied","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"that he is a strident critic of the Trump administration .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"\" I come really really hard against 45 , ''","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"he said .","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"referring to Trump , the 45th U.S. president .","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"`` I come really really hard against his administration ,","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"and I don ' t hold my tongue . \" .","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"@ JussieSmollett - what about MAGA and the tens of millions of people","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"you insulted with your racist and dangerous comments ! ?","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"# MAGA","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"February 21 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"During a press briefing later Thursday morning , Chicago law enforcement officials said","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"that Chicago police detectives interviewed more than 100 people","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"and reviewed dozens of police cameras","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"trying to get to the bottom of Smollett 's claims .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"\" \" How can an individual","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"who 's been embraced by the city of Chicago","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"turn around and slap everyone in the city in the face with these false claims ?","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"Johnson , a well-regarded and popular big city police chief and Chicago native , appeared genuinely aggrieved","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"as he described how ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Smollett took advantage of the pain of racism","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"to advance his career .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"`` Why would anyone use the symbol of a noose ''","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"to further his `` own public profile , ''","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Johnson wondered aloud .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"`` I 'm offended by what happened","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"and I 'm angry , ''","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"Johnson continued .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"`` This publicity stunt was a scar","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"that Chicago didn ' t own","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"and certainly didn ' t deserve . ''","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Johnson ,","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"who oversees one of the nation 's largest police departments in one of its most violent cities ,","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"seemed disheartened by all the attention","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"paid to the Smollett affair .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"\" The accusation within this phony attack received national attention for weeks , \"","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"Johnson told reporters during a press conference .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"\" Celebrities , news commentators and even presidential candidates weighed in on something","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"that was choreographed by an actor . ''","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"`` When you get the opportunity , ''","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"he said with a mixture of derision and frustration ,","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"`` the shooting victims and their families ?","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"Give them the same amount of attention . ''","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"Press Briefing :","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"Jussie Smollet is under arrest and in custody of detectives .","depth":7},{"id":162,"text":"At 9am at # ChicagoPolice Headquarters , Supt Eddie Johnson , Commander of Area Central Detectives Edward Wodnicki will brief reporters on the investigation prior to the defendants appearance in court .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"pic.twitter.com/9PSv8Ojec","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"2 - Anthony Guglielmi","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"( @ AJGuglielmi )","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"February 21 , 2019","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"After the press briefing ,","depth":5},{"id":168,"text":"20th Century Fox , the station","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"that airs `` Empire , ''","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"released a statement","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"which read ,","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"`` We understand the seriousness of this matter","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"and we respect the legal process .","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"We are evaluating the situation","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"and we are considering our options . ''","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"Smollett told police","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"he was attacked by two masked men near his apartment in Chicago .","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"The two men ,","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"Smollett initially said ,","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"shouted racist and homophobic slurs at him","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"as a rope was wrapped around his neck","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"and a chemical compound was poured on him .","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"The alleged assailants yelled `` MAGA country , '' a reference to President Donald Trump 's `` Make American Great Again '' slogan ,","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"police were told .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"\" \" Chicago trusted this young man .","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"We loved 'Empire , '","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"and we took this very seriously","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"that something this hateful could happen in our city .","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"In an interview with `` Good Morning America '' anchor Robin Roberts , Smollett said","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"he was heartbroken","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"when he found out","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"that people questioned his story .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"Asked why he would leave the rope draped around his neck","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"until police arrived","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"because he `` wanted them to see . ''","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"`` I was looking at myself ,","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"just like checking myself out , ''","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"he told Roberts .","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"`` I saw the bruise on my neck ,","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"you know ,","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"like the little --","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"the rope burn around my neck .","depth":13},{"id":203,"text":"So","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"when the police came","depth":16},{"id":205,"text":"I kept the clothes on ,","depth":16},{"id":206,"text":"I kept the rope on me . ...","depth":15},{"id":207,"text":"I mean ,","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"it was n't , like , wrapped around .","depth":16},{"id":209,"text":"But , yeah , it was around","depth":16},{"id":210,"text":"because I wanted them to see . ''","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"Asked why he wait until the second interview","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"to tell police","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"that the assailants yelled \" MAGA country \" at him during the attack ,","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"Smollett seemed to take offense at the insinuation .","depth":11},{"id":215,"text":"`` For me , the main thing was the idea","depth":15},{"id":216,"text":"that I somehow switched up my story ,","depth":16},{"id":217,"text":"you know ?","depth":16},{"id":218,"text":"And that somehow maybe I added a little extra trinket ,","depth":16},{"id":219,"text":"you know ,","depth":16},{"id":220,"text":"of the MAGA thing , ''","depth":15},{"id":221,"text":"Smollett said on .","depth":13},{"id":222,"text":"`` I did n't need to add anything like that .","depth":12},{"id":223,"text":"They called me a f -- -- ,","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"they called me a n -- -- .","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"There 's no which way","depth":13},{"id":226,"text":"you cut it . ''","depth":13},{"id":227,"text":"Johnson said on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"that Smollett 's seeming injuries from the incident also appeared to be phony .","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"\" The brothers had on gloves during the staged attack","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"where they -- they punched him a little bit ,","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"but","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"as far as we can tell ,","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"the scratches and bruising","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"that you saw on his face","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"was most likely self-inflicted . ''","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"Police identified and questioned two `` persons of interest ''","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"captured on surveillance video near the scene around the time of the alleged attack .","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"The men ,","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"who are brothers ,","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"were arrested on Feb. 13","depth":10},{"id":241,"text":"but then released without charges ,","depth":10},{"id":242,"text":"with police saying","depth":11},{"id":243,"text":"they were no longer considered suspects .","depth":11},{"id":244,"text":"While being questioned by investigators ,","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"the brothers claimed","depth":12},{"id":246,"text":"that Smollett paid them to help orchestrate and stage the crime","depth":13},{"id":247,"text":"after he became upset","depth":14},{"id":248,"text":"that a letter","depth":17},{"id":249,"text":"threatening him ,","depth":17},{"id":250,"text":"sent Jan. 22 to the Fox studio","depth":17},{"id":251,"text":"where `` Empire '' is filmed ,","depth":17},{"id":252,"text":"did not get enough attention ,","depth":15},{"id":253,"text":"sources told .","depth":10},{"id":254,"text":"On Wednesday , Smollett was charged with felony disorderly conduct","depth":11},{"id":255,"text":"for filing a false crime report .","depth":11},{"id":256,"text":"By that evening , police officially had classified the actor as a suspect in the ongoing investigation .","depth":11},{"id":257,"text":"Detectives subsequently presented evidence to a Cook County grand jury .","depth":11},{"id":258,"text":"`` That was a pretty hateful allegation ,","depth":11},{"id":259,"text":"and it really put a terrible look on Chicago , ''","depth":11},{"id":260,"text":"Guglielmi told ABC Chicago station WLS in a telephone interview Thursday morning .","depth":10},{"id":261,"text":"`` Chicago trusted this young man .","depth":10},{"id":262,"text":"We loved 'Empire , '","depth":11},{"id":263,"text":"and we took this very seriously","depth":12},{"id":264,"text":"that something this hateful could happen in our city . ''","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":529,"left":271,"right":528,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":266,"right":270,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":270,"left":2,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":3,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":4,"right":267,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":267,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":528,"left":390,"right":527,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":390,"left":274,"right":389,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":274,"left":273,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":273,"left":7,"right":272,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":272,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":389,"left":278,"right":388,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":277,"right":15,"r